title: Ded Peek Nangfah
overview: Long ago it was a custom for women to wait for a men to court first before being maried, however this is long gone and definitely not the case for the flight attendants of Nangfah Airlines. A rich and handsome co-pilot is caught between a cat fight of ladies who are trying to win his heart. Will he let himself be caught by one of them and if so, who would he choose?
